---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import PageHeader from '../components/PageHeader.astro';
import Cta from '../components/Cta.astro';

// Client copy — Jeanette, 2026-06-08 "final edit to publish the site": the Twelve Domains of Development.
// Names + descriptions are HER exact words (this page existed as a 12-card placeholder awaiting them); do
// not paraphrase. Intro/closing paragraphs below are also verbatim from that email.
const domains = [
  { name: 'Origins',       desc: 'Develops self-awareness and initiative, helping students recognize opportunities for growth and take the first step forward.' },
  { name: 'Foundations',   desc: 'Develops consistency and personal responsibility, creating habits that support long-term success.' },
  { name: 'Confidence',    desc: 'Develops self-trust through action, helping students engage challenges with greater courage and resilience.' },
  { name: 'Relationship',  desc: 'Develops connection and interpersonal awareness, strengthening the ability to work effectively with others.' },
  { name: 'Communication', desc: 'Develops clear expression and active listening, improving understanding, cooperation, and leadership.' },
  { name: 'Perspective',   desc: 'Develops adaptability and critical thinking, helping students respond thoughtfully rather than react impulsively.' },
  { name: 'Purpose',       desc: 'Develops direction and commitment, helping students align effort with meaningful goals.' },
  { name: 'Contribution',  desc: 'Develops service and responsibility, encouraging students to positively influence the people around them.' },
  { name: 'Principle',     desc: 'Develops integrity and decision-making, helping students act consistently even under pressure.' },
  { name: 'Exploration',   desc: 'Develops curiosity and lifelong learning, encouraging growth beyond familiar experiences.' },
  { name: 'Integration',   desc: 'Develops balance and self-governance, bringing knowledge, action, and character into alignment.' },
  { name: 'Resonance',     desc: 'Develops leadership through influence, helping students create positive impact within their families, communities, and professions.' },
];
---
<Base title="The Domains of Development — The Qi-House">
  <PageHeader
    eyebrow="Our Educational Model"
    title="The Domains of Development"
    subtitle="A practical framework for building confidence, focus, communication, and self-governance."
  />

  <section class="bg-stone">
    <div class="container-content py-section-sm lg:py-section">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-14 reveal space-y-5">
        <p class="text-lg text-slate/90">
          Real growth is more than the acquisition of a single skill. At Eight Hands Martial Arts Academy,
          development is approached as a whole-person process. Our educational model helps students build the
          awareness, discipline, communication, responsibility, and leadership necessary to navigate life's
          challenges with confidence and purpose.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate/90">
          The Twelve Domains represent interconnected areas of development. They are not ranks to achieve or
          stages to complete. Every student possesses the capacity for each domain, and growth occurs through
          learning when and how to apply the right capability to the situation at hand.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        {domains.map((d, i) => (
          <div class="reveal border border-navy/10 bg-white rounded-sm p-6 hover:border-gold transition-colors">
            <div class="eyebrow !text-slate-400 mb-2">Domain {String(i + 1).padStart(2, '0')}</div>
            <div class="font-display text-2xl text-navy mb-3">{d.name}</div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate/80 leading-relaxed">{d.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <p class="text-center text-slate/80 italic font-display text-xl mt-14 reveal max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Progress is not measured by how many domains a student can name, but by how effectively they can apply
        these capabilities in everyday life. Development becomes visible through the ability to remain present
        under pressure, adapt to changing circumstances, communicate effectively, and take responsibility for
        the outcomes one creates.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Cta title="See how the model develops you." text="The clearest way to understand our approach is to experience it. Schedule an assessment to discuss your goals and the pathway that fits them." />
</Base>
